{"tid":1680703,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人記得自己前日漏低嘢係地櫃呀","createTime":"2019-10-29T03:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T08:29:24.000Z","uid":295190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"88bdd835d9c31a4ad58b437e1880dd30c81d2ec3","tid":1680703,"uid":295190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:36:24.000Z","msg":"聽朋友講<br />\n話說尋日有幾個學生哥前日係旺角話要急住返屋企食飯喎<br />\n咁佢地就太心急所以漏低咗啲返學用品係某個地櫃到唔記得拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁佢見到就有幾多拎幾多<br />\n希望班學生哥可以見到個post 拎得返啲文具遲啲返學唔會無晒啲嘢讀唔到書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望有心人幫手推下幫啲學生哥喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58460c5ed77be5eff85012bfc3b7feadb6651ce9","tid":1680703,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:36:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyBfyPB.jpg&h=2708f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2f9c5a983765821ab7958b570205e6e77fddd9af","tid":1680703,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLdavJJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLdavJJ.gif&h=943b7306&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e59c89c9b31566eca4d10cf54af886dfc55f2f8","tid":1680703,"uid":295190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:15:53.000Z","msg":"推?"},{"pid":"927918f55e135965727a131be35756b41f6fbc34","tid":1680703,"uid":295190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:29:24.000Z","msg":"推？"}]}